gangsters who set up Track Two in Cuba.

997
01:09:22,870 --> 01:09:25,330
Oh, well, I know all about that.

998
01:09:25,420 --> 01:09:28,210
I don't understand it.
Track Two is Chile.

999
01:09:28,290 --> 01:09:32,880
<i>Yeah, Chile, Congo,
